Title: Working Stiffs
Plot: The team investigates the murder of Jason, a troubled computer geek working at a low-level casino support industry job who lures a colleague, Paulie, into a dangerous plan to make a working stiff's dream come true.
ParentalRatingReason: R16 Violence and content that may disturb
GuestStars: Tim Blake Nelson, Ben Feldman, Wayne Knight, Tracy Middendorf, Alyson Reed, Matt Doherty, Archie Kao, Larry Sullivan
